Module JNewton
Package crab.newton

Class Newton

java.lang.Object
crab.newton.Newton
public class Newton extends Object
Newton relies on preview features of the Java platform:
  • Newton refers to one or more preview APIs: MemorySegment, OfAddress, OfByte, OfDouble, OfFloat, OfInt, OfLong, OfShort, StructLayout.
Programs can only use Newton when preview features are enabled.
Preview features may be removed in a future release, or upgraded to permanent features of the Java platform.
The class that contains all the functions in the Newton Dynamics Physics Library.
